'''意大利音乐产业联盟'''（{{lang-it|Federazione Industria Musicale Italiana}}，簡稱：'''{{lang|it|FIMI}}'''）是[[意大利|意大利]]一個追蹤該國音樂唱片產業的一個組織，於1992年建立。<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://archiviostorico.corriere.it/1992/ottobre/25/Sanremo_gia_una_stonatura_co_0_9210257836.shtml | work = [[晚邮报|Corriere della Sera]] | author = Mario Luzzatto Fegiz | date = 1992-10-25 | title = Sanremo '93, già una stonatura | accessdate = 2017-03-22 | archive-date = 2015-09-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150930162740/http://archiviostorico.corriere.it/1992/ottobre/25/Sanremo_gia_una_stonatura_co_0_9210257836.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Rockol2002">{{Cite web | url = http://www.rockol.it/news-49125/Inchiesta-classifiche-Rockol--la-parola-a-Enzo-Mazza-%28FIMI%29 | publisher = rockol.it | accessdate = 2011-08-17 | title = Inchiesta classifiche Rockol: la parola a Enzo Mazza (FIMI) | date = 2002-11-26 | archive-date = 2012-03-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120318060204/http://www.rockol.it/news-49125/Inchiesta-classifiche-Rockol--la-parola-a-Enzo-Mazza-(FIMI) | dead-url = no }}</ref>該組織成立之後，許多廠牌陸續離開了原有組織意大利唱片業协会（{{lang|it|Associazione dei Fonografici Italiani}}）轉而與該組織合作。<ref name="Rockol2002"/>截至2011年，意大利音乐产业联盟以代表超過2500家唱片經營[[音樂產業|音樂產業]]。<ref name="FIMI"/>

意大利音乐产业联盟是[[國際唱片業協會|國際唱片業協會]]的一員。<ref name="FIMI">{{Cite web | url = http://www.fimi.it/profilo.php | publisher = Federation of the Italian Music Industry | accessdate = 2011-08-17 | title = FIMI – Profilo | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110810170223/http://www.fimi.it/profilo.php | archivedate = 2011-08-10 }}</ref>其成立的主要目的是保护意大利唱片產业的利益。<ref name="FIMI"/>

1995年3月，聯盟開始發佈意大利官方專輯榜單。1997年1月，聯盟又提供了單曲榜單。由於實體唱片市場的衰落，2008年1月1日，聯盟開始以[[數位音樂下載|數位下載]]榜單取代原有的實體單曲榜單。<ref name=Billboard>{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.biz/bbbiz/search/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1003696014 |title=Italy's Singles Chart Goes Digital |accessdate=2008-02-11 |last=Worden |first=Mark |date=2008-01-14 |work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]] |archive-date=2011-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110521192500/http://www.billboard.biz/bbbiz/search/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1003696014 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2011年7月，恩佐·馬薩確認成為聯盟的主席。<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.rockol.it/news-273865/FIMI-nella-continuit%C3%A0,-Enzo-Mazza-riconfermato-presidente- | publisher = Rockol.it | accessdate = 2011-08-17 | title = FIMI nella continuità, Enzo Mazza riconfermato presidente | date = 2011-07-29 | archive-date = 2012-03-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120318060221/http://www.rockol.it/news-273865/FIMI-nella-continuit%C3%A0,-Enzo-Mazza-riconfermato-presidente- | dead-url = no }}</ref>

